OL,5,CThis Evening and Tonight:FA bright end
OL,6,Fto the day then remaining dry
OL,7,Fovernight with long clear spells.
OL,8,FBecoming rather chilly overnight with
OL,9,Fsome patchy mist developing. Light
OL,10,Fwinds.
OL,11,
OL,12,CMonday:FEarly mist soon clearing then
OL,13,Fa dry day with long spells of
OL,14,Fsunshine. Becoming quite warm inland
OL,15,Fbut cooler with some mist along the
OL,16,Feast coast.
